lor="#FFFFFF">                   <td valign="top"> <p class="headline1">How to Vote From Home                     </p>                    <p><span class="headline2">Every state allows <em>absentee                       voting</em></span><br>                      <span class="bodyText"> In most cases, you fill out a ballot                       at home, then send it in before election day. However, rules                       vary. For instance, some states require you to meet specific                       requirements to be able to vote by absentee ballot.</span></p>                    <p class="headline2"><font color="#660000">&#8211;&gt; </font>Live                       outside the USA? <span class="bodyText"><a href="http://electionimpact.votenet.com/yourvotematters/ab_regform_fcpa.cfm" target="_blank">Click                       here to register to receive an absentee ballot</a>. </span></p>                    <p class="headline2"><font color="#660000">&#8211;&gt;</font>                       In the military? <span class="bodyText"><a href="http://www.myballot.mil" target="_blank">Click                       here to request and receive your absentee ballot via the                       Internet</a>. </span></p>                    <p><span class="headline1"><br>                      Click on your state below for more information about your                       absentee voting requirements.</span><span class="bodyBold"><br>                      </span>                       <!--image map-->                    </p>                    <p><img src="img/usamap.gif" width="400" height="240" usemap="#Map" border="0"><br>                      &nbsp;                       <map name="Map">                        <area target="new" shape="rect" coords="9,183,76,197" href="results.php?state=AK"" alt="Alaska" title="Alaska">                        <area target="new" shape="rect" coords="10,201,77,214" href="results.php?state=HI" alt="Hawaii" title